# ibinet-sdk Context

- This package is the shared source of truth for cross-app models, helpers, middleware, and services.
- Keep framework-agnostic package quality; avoid app-specific business logic unless it is intentionally shared.
- Do not add migrations here; shared schema is maintained mainly by IDC.
- Preserve helper APIs (`has()`, `setting()`, route helpers) and Blade directives because many apps depend on them.
- Maintain compatibility for critical services like `ApprovalService` and `TechnicianBorrowService`.
- Prefer extending existing `Ibinet\Models\*` conventions (UUIDs, SoftDeletes, activity logging patterns).
